SVANSAI Debugger Agent Full Bundle
This bundle gives you a single-pass file set so you do not have to keep updating the same files repeatedly.
Included
Electron app files for Apps + Network + Files + Sites bridge
Browser extension for real open-tab site scanning
FastAPI route file for the browser bridge
Put your existing assets here
`src/renderer/public/svdebugger.png`
`assets/icon.ico`
Backend router registration

```python
from browser_bridge_routes import router as browser_bridge_router
app.include_router(browser_bridge_router)
```

Load the browser extension
Open Chrome or Edge extensions page, enable Developer Mode, then load the `browser_extension` folder as an unpacked extension.
